welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Silver Firs, where the charm of our small town will capture your heart. Known for its picturesque landscapes and friendly community, we invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport serves primarily private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the hub for all flights and passenger services.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
terminals.description: The seaplane terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is where all seaplane flights arrive and depart.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport caters to private and corporate aircraft, providing exclusive services and facilities for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of Seattle-Tacoma International Airport, also known as Sea-Tac Airport. It houses most of the airport's facilities and services.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: Located north of the main terminal, this satellite terminal serves as a hub for Alaska Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: Located south of the main terminal, this satellite terminal serves as a hub for Delta Air Lines and its partners.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Simply select the network and accept the terms and conditions to connect.
